phrases: Oh, I am just talking to myself.
The more damage he takes, the stronger he gets!
Ranta, I am counting on you.
Do not die, Haruhiro, you idiot!
I have to keep fighting in a situation like this?
No, he is moving really slowly.
What is that supposed to mean?
I just could not accept Manato's death at that time yet.
Well, there was something I wanted to ask you.
WhatI guess they are pretty friendly.
Is it because I am a Dark Knight?
You are only calling me a caterpillar now.
I really need to get out of this mine.
No way, no way, no way, no way, no way.
Die and be in Skullhell-sama's embrace.
So I am a caterpillar after all?
O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection.
Let us go over our priorities again.
Our top priority is for all five of us to get back alive.
Yes, we will do as much as we can, but we cannot be reckless.
Um, you probably know that I do not like Ranta.
It hurts my feelings when he calls me flat-chested, and he does not stop even when I tell him to.
It is hard to like someone like that, even if you asked me to try.
But, if I were all alone in this mine, I would be really scared, you know?
And when I think about how Ranta must be feeling right now...
If he would die from something like this, he would have died many times by now.
Vice, Vice, Vice, Vice, Vice, Vice, Vice!
Not the time to think about Vices!
He is the only it could be.
He got up here after being surrounded like that?
It is pretty amazing if he did.
His strength to live is stronger than most, to say the least.
The rest of us do not have that kind of tenacity to live.
Flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest, flat-chest!
I should have fondled her flat chest!
Do not just call out to someone so suddenly.
You almost gave me a heart attack, idiot!
O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection.
Who do you think you are talking to, scum.
O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection.
Your eyes are all watery, though.
You do not have to get so mad.
We were able to see you alive again.
I wanted to see you guys again!
No way I wanted to see you again.
Wh-When I thought I would never see all your pretty little faces again, my chest
I will, and I will say it million times!
Do you want me to stop healing you?
Let us go back to Ortana.
It is been a long day, huh...
Do not let your guard down until we get back to Ortana.
I was thinking about what Ranta meant when he said, Are not you our leader?
Because to me, Manato was our leader.
And to be honest, there was something inside me that thought I had to become like Manato, but...
Manato said that everyone has strengths and weaknesses...
As for me, I have a lot of things that I am not good at and that I need to work on.
My comrades make up for those weaknesses by helping me out,
and maybe that is how we have found a balance in our party.
That is why I do not know if I am actually being a proper leader.
But if things are running smoothly, that is probably the most important thing.
Like for Ranta and me, if we can work well during a fight, it is all good.
That is because that is the most important thing.
I will not be able to use magic for a while.
At the most, I can cast one Cure.
I need to go meditate somewhere.
I do not really understand magic, but Shihoru looks drained, too.
We will try not to bother the Lesser Kobolds.
Death Spots gets stronger from the wounds!
That is the only thing we can do, but can we outrun him?
It will be impossible on this straight path.
Someone... at least one of us needs to stay.
Before I knew it, my body started moving.
Yes... get out of here... everyone.
Do not give up in a situation like this?
Merry... come back and cast Dispel on me, too.
Then, maybe we can meet again.
It is a battle of life and death...
So I am not going to give up, and I will keep living.
I will keep living until I die!
Ranta suggested to discuss how we should split it after you woke up.
He said it was because you are the leader.
You got a problem with that?
Oh yeah, and when we went back to get you
Oh, yeah... when you went back to get me.
You were lying next the Date Spots, you know.
Yeah, my sword was broken anyway, and it seemed wieldy so I thought I would try it out.
I cannot use it like this, though.
I was thinking of taking it to a swordsmith.
I guess we have decided on one of the ways we will be using the bounty on.
When it is done, we need to give it a cute name.
I-I guess it is kind of cute.
The slight weight and feeling of it settled onto me... and somewhere inside me, I felt calm.
I heard, I heard all about it, Haruhirocchi!
For what I did when Manato died.
No, you do not need to apologize.
I just... could not accept Manato's death yet... at that time.
So I should say thanks, Renji.
Has it been tough for you?
I am different from who I was yesterday.
I wonder what I will be like tomorrow.
Day by day, we live in the today and keep living...
As I continue living in this world...
The memories from what I should call the world I came from.
The solid feeling of the stone beneath me...
I now have things that I do not want to forget, and things that I should not forget.
And I do not plan to ever forget those things...
Having fun, laughing, getting hurt, and crying
Living in the presence of one another
The ever-changing twilight becomes a miracle
Once, I saw in the sky
The winds of the future blowing in my reflection
I am glad I can meet you again tomorrow
This long, long road I have walked
Will bring me to another new world
I have been through meetings and farewells
Days pass by one by one
With memories I will not forget anymore
Drawing what is happening now on the horizon
The next morning will bring tomorrow
Soon, moving forward and farther ahead
Going towards the future as I am now
I am glad I can meet you again tomorrow
This long, long road I have walked
Will bring me to another new world
